  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Veterinary Receptionist",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us</strong><br>\nWe are a newly established full-service veterinary clinic in <strong>Sembawang</strong>, seeking enthusiastic and committed individuals to join our growing team. This is a fantastic opportunity to build a rewarding career in the veterinary field while working alongside dedicated animal care professionals.</p>\n<p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong><br>\nWhile prior front desk or customer service experience is an advantage, it is not essential—we welcome applicants with the right attitude and a passion for learning.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Polite, professional, and enthusiastic demeanor</li>\n  <li>Strong multitasking skills and ability to work well in a team</li>\n  <li>Responsible, reliable, and efficient with time management</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal and communication (PR) skills</li>\n  <li>Competent in written and spoken English for client interactions</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office</li>\n  <li>Genuine passion for animal care and welfare</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>On-the-job training in all clinic systems and processes</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to learn from and work closely with experienced veterinary professionals</li>\n  <li>Exposure to animal care and the option to assist with animal patients if desired</li>\n  <li>A supportive and dynamic team environment with opportunities for growth</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are enthusiastic, compassionate, and eager to grow in the veterinary profession, we’d love to hear from you!</p>",
